<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Former Destiny Child member Kelly Rowland made an appearance in Beyonce's stunning new video for Brown Skin Girl that debuted just over a week ago.</p>

<p>And on Thursday Rowland was spotted taking care of some errands while out and about in Los Angeles.</p>

<p>She looked nearly unrecognizable wearing a protective mask, amid the still ongoing COVID-19 pandemic, and large, white-rimmed sunglasses that would have made a fashionista from the 1970s proud. </p>

<p>On the go: Kelly Rowland stepped out to take care of some errands in Los Angeles on Thursday</p>

<p>Between the sunglasses and mask, much of Rowland's face was covered up.</p>

<p>For the outing, she opted to wear a short-sleeve, baggy black dress that draped down to her ankles and nearly covered up her matching black sandals. </p>

<p>The Georgia native pulled her long raven tresses back into a tight bun and with a part in the middle.</p>

<p>Who's that girl? Rowland, 39,  looked nearly unrecognizable in retro white sunglasses, protective mask and a short-sleeve, baggy black dress that draped down to her ankles</p>

<p>Reality world: Rowland has spent a good deal of her time Down Under serving as a judge and a coach on The Voice Australia since 2017</p>

<p>Rowland, 39, has spent a good deal of her time Down Under serving as a judge and a coach on The Voice Australia since 2017. </p>

<p>Throughout her career, Rowland has sold over 30 million records as a solo artist, and another 60 million records during her run with Destiny's Child, which helped make them among the best-selling girl groups of all time, with hits like Say My Name and Bootylicious.</p>

<p>The group, that oftentimes featured Beyonce as the lead, released four studio albums beginning in 1997 until their disbandment in 2006. </p>

<p>Mega-stars: Rowland and Beyonce enjoyed massive success in Destiny's Child; she former group, that at the time included LeToya Luckett and LaTavia Roberson, are pictured in 1999</p>

<p>Rowland and Beyonce have remained friends and have reunited on various projects over the years, including her appearance Brown Skin Girl, which also featured the likes of Beyonce and Jay-Z's eight-year-old daughter Blue Ivy Carter, Naomi Campbell and Lupita Nyong'o.     </p>

<p>Along with her career in music, television and film, Rowland is a proud mother of five-year-old son Titan that she shares with her husband Tim Weatherspoon.</p>

<p>The couple reportedly started dating back in 2011, which led to the announcement of their engagement onThe Queen Latifah Show in December 2013.</p>

<p>They were eventually married in Costa Rica in May 2014.    </p>

<p>Special guest: Rowland made an appearance in Beyonce's stunning new video for Brown Skin Girl that debuted just over a week ago</p>

<p>Glowing; The pair could be seen hugging it out with big smiles on their faces</p>
